  "description": {
    "zh": "又见面了，我有件重要的事情，你可能会感兴趣。\n\n基本上就在刚才我们刚接到一个买家的交易，他在寻找一些……药物，大概是塔科夫这里TerraGroupTerraGroup集团的产品？哎呀，随便是啥，我不在乎他的背景或意图，我只知道他会支付足够的费用。\n\n现在我需要你带给我一些我目前没有的注射针剂，如果你能够帮忙的话，我会允许你从我们这边的库存拿一些特殊注射剂。你愿意接受这个任务吗？我会给你所需物品的清单，我就指望你了，士兵。",
    "en": "Hello again, I got something important, you might be interested.\n\nSo basically we just got contacted by a buyer that is looking for certain... drugs, here from Tarkov, Terragroup related goods i'm guessing? Well anyway, I don't care about his background or intentions, he will be paying enough for it.\n\nWhat I need from you know is to bring me some of these injectors that I don't have on me right now, I will give you access to our stock for some special injectors for that if you help. Are you in? I will give you the list of things that are needed, I will count on you soldier."
  },
